{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1672762268.120304", "card_id": "Q_576523800", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 455}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "乐视宣布实行四天半工作制，周三休息半天，如何看待这一举措？会被推广吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "乐视视频官微宣布：2023 年 1 月 1 日起，乐视将执行每周四天半工作制，每周三弹性工作半天。乐视在公告中表示，连续三年的疫情难免影响公司业务，所有员工都关心公司业绩，也更担心自己的生活。让人欣慰的是，在大家的努力下, 公司 2022 年业务总体平稳，经营业务实现了现金流平衡，并且前 3 季度虽有 5 周居家办公，整体业绩目标均如期达成。 来源：贝壳财经"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0e75495fae005665894e611ca1e59d7b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "960 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576523800"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IzcD356vr5eY/EAMaCDkwMzk3OTU1IOelz50GMEQ4/whAAHIJNTc2NTIzODAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1672762268.121314", "card_id": "Q_575083461", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 678}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么绝大多数小说、动画和电影在描写永生时都说是痛苦的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-560a44e6eb39ff73978f89328e156441_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "445 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/575083461"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IzcD356vr5eY/EAMaCDkwMDc3ODc1IN+9rJ0GMDA4vwhAAXIJNTc1MDgzNDYxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1672762268.1219287", "card_id": "Q_576510658", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 409}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "阳康以后，你还感觉有哪些不适？用了多久才完全恢复到自己从前的状态？"}, "ex